{"tid":1640640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅裝飾方法錯哂","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:59:02.000Z","uid":273621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0bdb2d68797884056fcb1d6f3daf3f6162ba04","tid":1640640,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到呢張文圖，製作非常精美，但反映左一個手足們裝飾既常見錯誤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KDxvPzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDxvPzP.jpg&h=9b65d086&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n就係裝飾品唔應該用「光復香港 時代革命」 / 「五大訴求 缺一不可」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要寫番<strong>點解</strong>幫佢裝飾啊</span><br />\n<br />\n到底係因為佢抹黑手足所以我地以德報怨幫佢裝飾？定係因為佢撐警，我地要多謝佢？<br />\n唔寫清楚既話其他商鋪同街坊點知點先可以獲得免費裝飾 / 裝修服務啊？<br />\n唔寫清楚老一輩會諗起<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅衛兵</strong></span>架！<br />\n紅衛兵咁老土你叫人點撐你啊，再加上對家依家派人扮手足裝修，好多人會比對家呃到，我地既裝飾 / 裝修要做得專業d先唔會比人扮到。"},{"pid":"ccf6e08ae66457c69d46d8cb05f8ddd64bec84bf","tid":1640640,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"30f8b57b5ea3927a22f6188e6ae5a40679be1c6a","tid":1640640,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ba9131ee1d240a2dde29c507ae0e5ea3f007ae13","tid":1640640,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8be29f185e33681c8889e7d82995f9294d95aaa7","tid":1640640,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffe22be5049f9dda3493e26007394f0a6a207a1d","tid":1640640,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"push"}]}